<div id="pf32" class="pf w1 h5" data-page-no="32"><div class="pc pc32 w1 h5"><div class="t m72 x42 h47 y45d ff1 fs26 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What Adventists Believe </div><div class="t m226 x40 h15 y1c7 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">During the third and fourth quarters of 1988, Sabbath Schools </div><div class="t m51d x5f h15 y664 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">around the world will turn temporarily from the Bible book cur-</div><div class="t m49f x5f h15 y665 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">riculum we have been studying. In order to revitalize our under-</div><div class="t m259 x5f h15 y1c9 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">standing of the fundamental beliefs of the Seventh-day Adventist </div><div class="t me7 x5f h15 y1ca ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Church, we will study one of the 27 statements of belief each Sab-</div><div class="t mbf x5f h15 y666 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">bath over a two-quarter period. </div><div class="t m3ae x40 h15 y306 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But there is more to this unique approach than reviewing our </div><div class="t m1da x5f h15 y667 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beliefs. Not only will you become more familiar with the teachings </div><div class="t m51e x5f h15 y668 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of your church but you also will be learning how to share your </div><div class="t m14f x5f h15 y669 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beliefs with those who wish to know more about them. </div><div class="t m20a x40 h15 y1cf ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Watch for additional information that will give you guidance on </div><div class="t m51f x5f h15 y66a ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">how to combine your study of these lessons with supplemental out-</div><div class="t m15a x5f h15 y1d2 ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reach tools such as doctrinal tracts, books, Bible lessons, and mis-</div><div class="t m1fa x5f h15 y66b ff2 fs9 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sionary literature. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
